        <p>It is up to you! Once your produce your own light show creation, now you need to showcase it to the world! The more shares, views, likes, and comments your light show earns, the greater your chance of winning! In the event of a tie, the finalists will be judged by DPS' own lighting design team.</p>
        <div classs="row">
