            <p>Participants may create their light show remotely on their own computer system or in person at the DPS booth in the RICHELIEU ROOM on March 24th and 25th. Entries must be received by noon, <strong>Wednesday March 25th 2015</strong> with the winner chosen at the DPS booth at the <strong>Deauville Beach Resort Hotel at 3pm</strong> that same day.</p>
            <p>Must be present at WMC 30 and the DPS booth to win.</p>
